title: Check Point Firewalls: Power Supply
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/checkpoint
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

item:
 Index of the power supply

description:
 This check monitors the health of the power supplies in checkpoint firewalls.
 The resulting state is determined by mapping the reported device status to a
 monitoring state via the rule "Check Point powersupply".

 By default, the status "Up" results in {OK}. Any other status, including
 "Present", results in {CRIT} unless explicitly configured otherwise,
 to be backward compatible.


discovery:
 One service is created for each power supply.
